      inverse ratio ventilation had been improve the oxygenation and respiratory mechanics during
      care of ARDS patients or during general anesthesia. We hypothized inverse ratio ventilatio
      could improve the oxygenation and respiratory mechanics on the obese patient also.
    </textblock>
